                  <td class="p-4 text-gray-200">API pricing</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQs -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-6">FAQs</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3">How does RAG AI handle sensitive or confidential documents?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                RAG systems implement enterprise-grade security including document-level access controls, encryption at rest and in transit, and audit logging. The AI only accesses documents that users have permission to view, maintaining existing security hierarchies. On-premises deployments ensure sensitive data never leaves your infrastructure.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3">What's the difference between RAG and traditional enterprise search?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                Traditional enterprise search returns lists of potentially relevant documents that users must manually review. RAG AI retrieval provides direct, synthesized answers by combining information from multiple sources, significantly reducing the time from query to actionable insight. Users get answers, not just links.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-3">How accurate are RAG AI responses compared to human experts?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                Studies show RAG AI systems achieve 90-95% accuracy on factual questions when properly implemented, often matching or exceeding human expert performance for routine queries. For complex analysis requiring judgment, RAG provides comprehensive background information that enhances human decision-making rather than replacing it.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="glass-morphism p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-4">
            Implement RAG AI Document Retrieval Today
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Transform your organization's knowledge access with cutting-edge RAG technology. 
            Get expert consultation on RAG implementation strategies and best practices.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <button class="bg-primary text-black py-3 px-8 rounded-lg font-orbitron font-bold hover:bg-primary/80 transition-all duration-300">
              Schedule RAG Consultation
            </button>
            <button class="border border-primary/30 text-primary py-3 px-8 rounded-lg font-orbitron font-bold hover:bg-primary/10 transition-all duration-300">
              Download RAG Implementation Guide
            </button>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Related Articles -->
        <section class="mt-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-6">Related Articles</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <a href="/blog/ai-document-management-system" class="glass-morphism p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 block">
